final_desc: - Lain-lain :Benang dan tali karet, ditutupi tekstil; benang tekstil, dan strip serta sejenisnya dari pos 54.04 atau 54.05, diresapi, dilapisi,ditutupi atau disarungi dengan karet atau plastik.;- Other :Rubber thread and cord, textile covered; textile yarn, and strip and the like of heading 54.04 or 54.05, impregnated, coated, covered or sheathed with rubber or plastics.
